               <t:note>
                  <t:date type="foundation" notBefore="1600" notAfter="1700">1600-1700</t:date>
                  <t:desc type="foundation">Local tradition claims the foundation in the time of the Aksumite king Sälʿadoba.</t:desc>
                  <t:ab type="history">Dabr. By the time of the visit the church was under construction. The old building was dismantled, with the exception of the sunctuary, and a new building was being built around. 
</t:ab>
                  <t:ab type="description">13 Mss., items recorded: <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESdmd001">DMD-001</t:ref> "Vita of Täklä Haymanot, Vita of Ewostatewos"; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESdmd002">DMD-002</t:ref> "Synaxarion (September)"; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESdmd003">DMD-003</t:ref> "Four Gospels"; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESdmd004">DMD-004</t:ref> "Story of St. Mary"; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESdmd005">DMD-005</t:ref> "Missal"; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESdmd006">DMD-006</t:ref> "Vita of Gäbrä Mänfäs Qǝddus"; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESdmd007">DMD-007</t:ref> "The Book of the Funeral Rite"; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESdmd008">DMD-008</t:ref> "Homily of St. Michael"; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESdmd009">DMD-009</t:ref> "Homily of the Saviour of the World"; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESdmd010">DMD-010</t:ref> "Miracles of John"; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESdmd011">DMD-011</t:ref> "The Book of the Chants"; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESdmd012">DMD-012</t:ref> "Synoptic Lectionary for the Year"; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESdmd013">DMD-013</t:ref> "Vita of Kiros"</t:ab>
             
